    <p>Zl 2: Spr 20,10</p>
    <p>Zl 7: 1Sam 4,19</p>
    <p>Zl 8: Est 2,15</p>
    <p>Zl 9: Gen 32,31</p>
   </div>
   <div type='commentary' subtype='Stilmittel'>
    <head>Stilmittel</head>
